      "content": "it just feels like a loop. no matter what i do, i'm just making it worse for everyone. i'm just a burden and a joke to them. honestly, sometimes i think the only thing that would actually make the noise stop—the judging, the talking, the feeling like i'm constantly failing—is if i just wasn't here anymore. like, wouldn't it just be easier for everyone if i just disappeared?",
